Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.94,0:01:35.64,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}知晓你的强大的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.00,0:01:41.42,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}人的希望  无名之人
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.72,0:01:46.22,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}赞颂你的内心吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.49,0:01:52.08,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}淡淡的小花们
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.41,0:01:57.22,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}坚韧不挠的藤蔓的形状
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.88,0:02:02.64,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}怀中藏有刺的影子
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.11,0:02:09.62,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}各自怀着不可言喻的昨天
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.62,0:02:13.37,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}向天空而去
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.77,0:02:18.83,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}只要生命还在  就喊出愿望吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.14,0:02:24.33,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}心意终将贯穿星辰
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.55,0:02:29.62,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}在漫长又短暂的时间的尽头
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.93,0:02:32.17,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}你生存过的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.07,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}证据会
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.63,0:02:37.05,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}顶起土壤
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.38,0:02:39.71,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}明日发芽
